title: Taking Care Of Yourself | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Taking Care Of Yourself | Joel Osteen
description:
Don’t let yourself get depleted by life’s demands. When you make taking care of yourself a priority, you’ll be better equipped to take hold of everything God has for you. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
